t: Kodi iwo sadayende padziko lapansi ndi kuona zimene zidawachitikira anthu amene adalipo kale pamene mitundu ya anthuwo idali yamphamvu kuposa iwo? Kulibe chinthu kumwamba kapena padziko lapansi chimene chingakhumudwitse Mulungu chifukwa Iye amadziwa chilichonse ndipo ndi mwini mphamvu zonse